videos.description: Ruthy Hebard makes her 31st consecutive made field goal, which extend field goal record in men or women's college basketball.
videos.headline: Hebard continues record with jumper

videos.description: Jordin Canada sets up Japreece Dean who drains a 3-pointer to make it a close game in the fourth quarter despite trailing by 19.
videos.headline: UCLA answers with big 3-pointer from Dean

videos.description: Oregon forces a turnover and Satou Sabally drains a 3-pointer on the other end giving her 23 points.
videos.headline: Oregon pumps up crowd with steal and score

videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu makes a long jumper in overtime and No. 8 Oregon holds on at home vs. No. 10 UCLA.
videos.headline: Ionescu jumper secures win for Oregon

videos.description: Oregon head coach Kelly Graves said the toughness his team showed down the stretch is what you need in a championship caliber team therefore he was happy to see it tonight.
videos.headline: Graves proud to see toughness in win over UCLA
